1. Ona je odlučila da promeni *situaciju* (She decided to change the situation).
2. On je uspeo da se izbori sa *situacijom* (He managed to cope with the situation).
3. Njihov odnos je postao neizdrživa *situacija* (Their relationship has become an unbearable situation).
4. Ona je bila u nezavidnoj *situaciji* (She was in an unenviable situation).
5. On je gledao u *situaciju* sa optimizmom (He was looking at the situation with optimism).